data.description:
Stunning home with 4 bedrooms, 4 full bathrooms, home office, media room and game room. It has a an open concept which is great for family gatherings. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances including dishwasher, stove, microwave. The living room has a lovely wood burning fireplace, the backyard is spacious with a covered patio. The master closet has walk-in sensor lighting and intalled shelves and drawers for excellent organization. The home is located in Artesia Community feeding into Prosper ISD schools. Walking distance to the community pool and playground. This home is ready to move in and awaiting it's new family.

All information deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buye's and Buyer's agent to verify all data. Seller will let the refridgerator, washer, and dryer convey with the property with full price offer. Seller is also open to selling the furniture. Buyer will have to purchase a new survey.
